271
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,320
Hia Tai!

272
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:14,480
Hia Tai! Hia Tai.

273
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:17,960
Hia Tai that! It’s always about Hia Tai!

274
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:21,960
Let me ask you straight.

275
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:25,840
Have you ever cared about me by yourself? Just once?

276
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:30,840
All you do is use Hia Tai as an excuse.

277
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,720
Stop yelling at me, Jun!

278
00:28:35,600 --> 00:28:38,200
No. Let go!

279
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:45,840
