288
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:37,280
Don’t forget—you’re just the guy who taught me about sex.

289
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,960
You have no right to act like that.

290
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:46,760
Jun.

291
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,920
And another thing...

292
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:57,680
Every time we sleep together, it’s because you wanted it!!

293
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:12,320
And I was just the idiot who let you fool me.

294
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:34,280
From now on.

295
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:40,000
You and I—we’re done. I don’t care what it’s about.

296
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:48,120
You won’t have to deal with a kid like me ever again.

297
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:58,000
And just so you know...

298
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,200
I hate you.

299
00:31:09,280 --> 00:31:11,520
Shit! P’Sorn!

300
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,920
Hey, where’d you go last night?

301
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:49,160
I told you, didn’t I? Don’t drive drunk.

302
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:54,640
I wasn’t drunk, bro. I went out with Jun.

303
00:31:55,720 --> 00:31:59,160
Try to keep that kid in check. He’ll go off the rails when he grows up.

304
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:06,760
Bro…

305
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:08,040
Hmm?

306
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,600
