314
00:32:55,600 --> 00:33:02,640
You sent the wrong order. If I sent this to the client, what then?
Pay attention, man.

315
00:33:07,360 --> 00:33:10,040
Did Tai call you?

316
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:11,640
Yeah, he did.

317
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:15,360
What about Jun?

318
00:33:17,280 --> 00:33:19,000
Why should I tell you?

319
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:24,000
