467
00:52:44,000 --> 00:52:45,480
So tiny and squishy.

468
00:52:50,280 --> 00:52:52,680
Here, here—take this.

469
00:52:59,680 --> 00:53:01,800
Let’s toast.

470
00:53:25,520 --> 00:53:29,640
Come on, Tai. Just tell me where Jun is.

471
00:53:30,120 --> 00:53:33,520
Hia, I’m not trusting a guy like Sorn. No way.

472
00:53:34,560 --> 00:53:35,960
No way... Hia Sorn?

473
00:53:36,960 --> 00:53:39,960
I caught you. Did you ever even miss me?

474
00:53:39,960 --> 00:53:40,960
Obviously not.

475
00:53:41,480 --> 00:53:42,680
Even if you didn’t… I missed you.
